<p>From what I've seen, this is one of the single most divisive issues between site members in terms of canon. This single issue really is the dividing line between an amoral and deontologist Foundation and a compassionate and regretful Foundation.</p>
<p>I honestly just omit the &quot;terminate at the first of the month&quot; from my headcanon entirely.</p>

