			<div class="content" id="post-content-1883439">
									

<p>My reply to Huitzil:<br />
Point A: Light amnestics.<br />
Point B: I would argue that they're doing it for the greater good, taking the people that have no one left for them, but it all really comes down to head canon.<br />
Point C: Also up to head canon. I would think there employing several methods in obtaining D-Class, including death row inmates and offering &quot;jobs&quot; to the homeless.</p>
<p>And I agree, monthly termination is pretty stupid, and I don't believe in it; this is also up to head canon. I <em>do</em> like to think that they're using a massive amount of amnestics (where they're getting it from, I'll leave that up for your imagination) to reuse each person.</p>

